    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i have this insanely bad headache right now, like its the worst one i've ever had by far. it came on really fast. i also noticed my left eye looks a bit different, like the lid is drooping a little. do u think it could just be a huge migraine coming on? i have some prescription meds for migraines i can take if u think that'll help",
