      "content": "i hear u, but honestly i've had huge migraines before and they felt pretty bad too. do u think if i just take an extra dose of my migraine meds and sleep it off, it would be okay? like, if i just take a double dose of sumatriptan it might make the headache go away faster so i don't have to go to the hospital. what do u think?",
